Designed and built by @ramtin_ray_nosrati , comes one of the most anticipated & mesmerizing projects in Los Angeles for $44,000,000.

Towering gracefully above LA’s dazzling city lights, this newly built smart home of sweeping picturesque vistas throughout (including unobstructed Getty, city and ocean views), expansive & flat over 30,000 square foot exterior living space, striking water features, and a vast array of exquisite amenities delivers effortless resort-style living and elevated entertainment that will continually wow you and your guests alike.

Listed at $44,000,000
